Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I am saying that it is not good to make such a requirement. In most of the campus, you need to share with your roommates, which someone may feel not happy with. And there are no kitchens in some colleges, so it is not convinent for people who cook themselves.